name: Norwegian Air Shuttle 737-8JP [LN-NGK] Landing and Takeoff at Krakow ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everyone, here's another video from Krakow, featuring a Norwegian Air Shuttle Boeing 737-800 landing and taking off from Krakow's John Paul II International Airport. I've only ever seen Norwegian's 787s but not their 737-800s, so this was a nice surprise. Hope you enjoy, and sorry for the shakiness, and for the rain on the windows during the departure. 

I've also launched a brand new channel website! Check it out: https://www.dude8472productions.com

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
____________________________________________________

FLIGHT INFO
Airline: Norwegian Air Shuttle (NAX/DY)
Aircraft: Boeing 737-800
Aircraft Name: "Johan Falkberget"
Engines: 2x CFMI CFM56-7B26E
Registration: LN-NGK
Route: CPH-KRK-CPH
Callsign: Nor Shuttle ????
Runway used: 25
Taxiway(s) used: A, C, RW07/25 (Aircraft had to backtrack the runway that day due to construction on the normal taxiway used for takeoffs)
FlightAware: http://flightaware.com/live/flight/LNNGK
